================================
 PROGRAMS FOR DEBIAN 8 V1.0 (EN)
================================

About Script:

  This script has the idea to help users both beginners and smart users. Its operation is simple and intuitive. 
Using only bash and the graphical interface add-on "dialog".

Please send me feedback for improvements and corrections of minor errors that have gone unnoticed.
Thank you all!

Acess to: www.vivaolinux.com.br

Be Free Use Linux!


HOW TO USE?

1 - Download: https://codeload.github.com/KelvinFerraz/ProgramsforDebian/zip/master

2 - Extrat to file: 
	$unzip ProgramsforDebian-master.zip

3 - Enter in directory ProgramsforDebian-master: 
	$cd ProgramsforDebian-master

4 - Permission on file using a root: "ProgramsDebianJessie.sh" : 
	#chmod +x ProgramsDebianJessie.sh

5 - This Script run just to root: 
	#./ProgramsDebianJessie.sh


